snippet.title: Amber Heard Receives Restraining Order Against Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
The stories people are buzzing about.

Johnny Depp's soon to be ex-wife, Amber Heard, has filed a domestic violence restraining order against the movie star. CBSN's Reena Ninan has the details.

Amber Heard requested a domestic abuse restraining order against her husband, Johnny Depp. A judge granted Heard's request- which requires Depp to stay .
